trans-unit.source: Sinapsi collects the news published by the Catalan educational centers on their websites. Makes visible most of the work developed by the centers and seeks to promote synergies between them.
trans-unit.target: Sinapsi recull les notícies que publiquen els centres educatius catalans a les seves pàgines web. Fa visible la major part del treball desenvolupat pels centres i busca promoure sinergies entre ells.
